These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: cola, mirinda
Movie-Genre: martial-arts, comedy
Sport: water-polo, biathlon
Transport: ship, scooter
1. Transport:scooter is on the left or right of Sport:biathlon##3
2. Beverage:mirinda is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:comedy == Beverage:cola##1
4. Transport:scooter is on the right of Transport:ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | cola  | mirinda   |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy     | martial-arts   |
| Sport         | biathlon | water-polo |
| Transport     | ship | scooter    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
Food: peas, carrot
Movie-Genre: thriller, drama
Pet: chinchilla, hamster
Transport: ship, quad-bike
1. Pet:hamster is in an odd position##4
2. Movie-Genre:thriller == Transport:quad-bike##1
3. Food:carrot is on the right of Movie-Genre:drama##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | peas     | carrot |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | thriller  |
| Pet           | hamster         | chinchilla     |
| Transport     | ship   | quad-bike    |

